        <updateDate>2015-10-19T13:52:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Save our Bays Act </strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a new tax credit, through 2020, for developing and implementing a plan to address non-point pollution carried by surface water runoff on real property located in the United States within the boundaries of an estuary of national significance. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
